{"title":"心事（二首）","authors":["范方"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":4,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"心事（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"范方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成败就是那么回事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正如左脚与右脚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前步与后步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热血与酒是兄弟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豪情无关"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听说　王维那股青烟很直"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落日很圆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长河在下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而我们　是生长在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地平线上一个永动的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车轮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偶及"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是一把攀不着枝丫而坠入江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心的秋叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涟漪没有回声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满目年轮飞旋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不论繁花千树云一朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"至此　都被凌厉的风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逼成　雁叫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而我在两天呕出的是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一堆石头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"至少也能感染那片苍白的月色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在夕暮中　激变成千山　大火"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}